Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:11:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we wait until the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls he the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been a good girl today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, is that your...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry that l dragged you around all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm staying over lto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, lto, my friend from High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l missed the last train, there's nothing l can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will come home tomorrow, l promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going back to my room to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was a tiring day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She acts like she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be all right, going back to Namikaze City by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you wouldn't call me again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry to call you late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you wearing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not saying we should dress fancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but let's plan ahead so we at least match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry to tell you this the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't make it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to finish a big project for the School Festival, and l can't skip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will make it up to you, l promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will have to buy me a very nice meal when l see you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l was in the fifth grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my parents got divorced because my father had an affair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since l was very small...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my father had gone out with many women.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought it was quite natural that my parents got divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was taken by my mother, since then, l haven't seen my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't think l wanted to see someone who betrayed my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l learned that my father was living in this area of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, l've been thinking about it ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should hate my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should disrespect my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l knew that l shouldn't, but l wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother and l have had a very difficult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, my father has such a happy family now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always wanted to see your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happy that your father is living happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, l know l would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...happy for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when l think about his happy wife and daughter, l can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato, make me feel better...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put in little Masato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei is so attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe she's the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sex is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so good, Masato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato, it's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold back, hold back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Chihiro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's date was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lshimaru-san, do you have a plan after work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to use the extra ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, l slept with Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so unfaithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you regretting that you slept with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fool around, you're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will say good-bye to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do it one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to stay in good shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we can't let what happened be just a one night stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already hard as a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harlem Heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's just too bad that l'm the one coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ticket's extra, l'm happy to go with someone with the same taste in music.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can have a date with Fukuroi-kun anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should enjoy going out with lshimaru-san today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lshimaru-san is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't do anything to upset anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l shouldn't be feeling bad about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you take the next train, you'll get back to Namikaze City by late afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not drop any clues about what we did last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still regretting that you've slept with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.32,0:23:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking so miserable, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just walked passed my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She saw us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you explain it to her then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:24:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because l slept with you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.63,0:24:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and apologize to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall l say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her the truth if you can't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you really love her, she will able to feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.89,0:24:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.39,0:24:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking forward to that concert and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.26,0:24:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.83,0:24:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.97,0:24:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you went home by yourself, l won't feel like listening to the music alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.21,0:24:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.65,0:24:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.28,0:24:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to the concert with some other guy because l canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.23,0:25:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, lshimaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.43,0:25:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm feeling better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.13,0:25:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.00,0:25:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm really sorry about the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.30,0:25:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.14,0:25:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.27,0:25:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he really be her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.24,0:25:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro wouldn't secretly be going out with another guy, would she?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.04,0:25:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Chihiro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.91,0:25:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.68,0:25:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seems too sudden but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.78,0:25:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.78,0:25:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know you have a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.88,0:25:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l need to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.55,0:25:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.92,0:25:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.66,0:25:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l can't trust Fukuroi-kun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.57,0:25:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lshimaru-san is nice and he will be more faithful to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.79,0:26:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, but no...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.02,0:26:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.46,0:26:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.13,0:26:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.07,0:26:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.00,0:26:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.14,0:26:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.07,0:26:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
